commit.message:
Makefile.in (bitmap.o, [...]): Update dependencies.

	* Makefile.in (bitmap.o, ebitmap.o, et-forest.o): Update
	dependencies.
	(sreal.o, statistics.o, stringpool.o): Likewise.

From-SVN: r166800

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2010-11-16  Nathan Froyd  <froydnj@codesourcery.com>
+
+	* Makefile.in (bitmap.o, ebitmap.o, et-forest.o): Update
+	dependencies.
+	(sreal.o, statistics.o, stringpool.o): Likewise.
+
 2010-11-16  Richard Guenther  <rguenther@suse.de>
 
 	PR tree-optimization/44545

 	$(TREE_H) $(GGC_H) $(GGC_INTERNAL_H) gt-stringpool.h $(CPPLIB_H) $(SYMTAB_H)

    $(LIBFUNCS_H) $(EXCEPT_H) $(RECOG_H) $(TOPLEV_H) $(DIAGNOSTIC_CORE_H) \

 dominance.o : dominance.c $(CONFIG_H) $(SYSTEM_H) coretypes.h $(TM_H) $(RTL_H) \

    insn-config.h reload.h $(FUNCTION_H) $(TM_P_H) $(GGC_H) \
